sources.title: The Last Starship | FULL MOVIE | Post-Apocalyptic Sci-Fi
sources.description:
As war is raging in a post-apocalyptic world, the survivors are hunted by a giant monster and attacked by an army of zombies and ancient machines of war.

#thriller #action #movie #scifi #apocalypse #postapocalyptic #starship #space #spacetravel #spaceship #orbit #interstellar #bmovie #zombiesurvival #kaiju #giantmonster #creaturefeature

metadata.Plot: This was evidently a pilot. Did anything ever come of it?Interesting enough to watch to the end and better than most current sci fy channel movies..but C grade. Especially because there was no ending...just hoping for more episodes so that the story could continue.Loved the multi language structure...they relly wanted to sell this series somehere....an any country would do.
metadata.Actors: Grace Byers, Jalyn Hall, Jack Coleman
